WEBVTT

00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:14.740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

00:01:31.519 --> 00:01:32.319
San Gou

00:01:35.040 --> 00:01:35.719
The Fool

00:01:36.120 --> 00:01:36.719
Come back

00:01:37.319 --> 00:01:38.400
He killed Tongtong

00:01:38.519 --> 00:01:39.680
I'm not The Fool.

00:01:40.280 --> 00:01:41.079
Tongtong isn't dead

00:01:43.200 --> 00:01:44.040
Tongtong isn't dead

00:01:46.079 --> 00:01:47.040
Then I'd be The Fool.

00:01:53.519 --> 00:01:54.879
To see an Immortal and not bow

00:01:55.480 --> 00:01:56.319
is a capital offense.

00:01:57.840 --> 00:01:58.480
Lao An

00:02:00.719 --> 00:02:02.120
I'm getting old

00:02:03.120 --> 00:02:03.840
Xiao Wu

00:02:04.040 --> 00:02:05.359
I might not outlive you

00:02:31.039 --> 00:02:32.199
Qian is Heaven

00:02:32.520 --> 00:02:33.400
Open Gate

00:02:33.639 --> 00:02:34.599
of Metal

00:02:46.159 --> 00:02:47.400
This Divine Blessing of yours

00:02:47.599 --> 00:02:48.479
is really something.

00:02:49.400 --> 00:02:50.439
Xun is Wind

00:02:50.639 --> 00:02:51.360
Startling Gate

00:02:51.439 --> 00:02:52.000
Speed

00:03:24.680 --> 00:03:25.879
A mortal martial art

00:03:26.199 --> 00:03:27.199
Bajiquan

00:03:29.680 --> 00:03:30.599
Please enlighten me.

00:03:34.639 --> 00:03:35.560
Are you sure

00:03:36.159 --> 00:03:38.439
you two, other than Su Yang,

00:03:38.479 --> 00:03:39.479
are the strongest?

00:03:48.599 --> 00:03:50.919
If my Spiritual Energy hadn't been depleted for years,

00:03:50.919 --> 00:03:52.360
leaving me with barely a tenth of my power,

00:03:52.439 --> 00:03:54.000
how could I suffer such humiliation?

00:03:55.280 --> 00:03:56.800
Even just finding my Immortal Artifact

00:03:57.199 --> 00:03:58.840
would let me slaughter you all with ease

00:03:58.919 --> 00:04:01.199
This elbow strike can crack metal and stone

00:04:01.560 --> 00:04:02.919
But his body's toughness

00:04:04.120 --> 00:04:05.759
is even more absurd than metal and stone

00:04:06.000 --> 00:04:08.680
How could you even comprehend an Immortal?

00:04:08.840 --> 00:04:09.520
Immortal

00:04:09.879 --> 00:04:11.000
Is this what you mean?

00:04:12.520 --> 00:04:13.360
Kid

00:04:13.719 --> 00:04:14.719
Watch closely

00:04:15.159 --> 00:04:17.560
This is how a Dharma Form is used

00:04:38.879 --> 00:04:39.879
People of the Same Origin

00:04:40.519 --> 00:04:41.800
The ancient texts record that

00:04:42.120 --> 00:04:44.160
devouring a Celestial Seed from

00:04:44.480 --> 00:04:45.639
People of the Same Origin is a shortcut

00:04:45.959 --> 00:04:46.959
to grow ever stronger.

00:04:47.120 --> 00:04:48.519
Such a rare occurrence

00:04:49.920 --> 00:04:51.360
actually happened right here.

00:05:18.800 --> 00:05:19.720
Damn it

00:05:20.199 --> 00:05:22.000
You care about that child, don't you?

00:05:24.600 --> 00:05:25.639
In that case,

00:05:26.040 --> 00:05:27.879
I'll take you out first for an appetizer.

00:05:28.680 --> 00:05:29.319
Tongtong

00:05:31.240 --> 00:05:31.639
Go!

00:05:31.639 --> 00:05:32.279
You have a death wish!

00:05:34.040 --> 00:05:34.920
Trying to run?

00:05:35.600 --> 00:05:37.519
Do you really think This Immortal is a pushover?

00:05:38.240 --> 00:05:38.959
Wang Qiusheng

00:05:41.120 --> 00:05:41.759
Where is he?

00:05:42.360 --> 00:05:42.959
Somebody!

00:05:54.839 --> 00:05:55.639
Qiu Ge

00:05:57.279 --> 00:05:58.360
Who got hit by mistake?

00:05:58.759 --> 00:05:59.879
Don't blame me.

00:06:22.519 --> 00:06:23.639
That close? Do you have a death wish?

00:06:24.160 --> 00:06:25.240
No wonder they call you Little Madman

00:06:26.240 --> 00:06:26.879
Tongtong

00:06:31.879 --> 00:06:32.319
Tongtong

00:06:32.319 --> 00:06:34.480
Aren't you afraid that thing'll blow up in your mouth?

00:06:34.759 --> 00:06:36.279
There's still a layer of syrup, right?

00:06:36.279 --> 00:06:37.040
It won't explode.

00:06:37.360 --> 00:06:37.879
Also

00:06:38.000 --> 00:06:39.240
I'm not called Little Madman

00:06:39.600 --> 00:06:40.480
I have a name

00:06:40.680 --> 00:06:41.680
My name is Qiu Ge

00:06:48.439 --> 00:06:49.519
How's Tongtong?

00:06:49.800 --> 00:06:50.399
She's fine

00:06:50.839 --> 00:06:51.560
Still unconscious

00:06:51.920 --> 00:06:54.000
Better she doesn't see something like this

00:06:54.399 --> 00:06:55.120
Insane

00:06:56.160 --> 00:06:58.000
This world has truly gone insane

00:06:59.560 --> 00:07:01.480
They even dare attack an Immortal

00:07:14.680 --> 00:07:15.439
The Fool

00:07:15.720 --> 00:07:16.519
Attack!

00:07:17.879 --> 00:07:18.480
The Fool

00:07:19.279 --> 00:07:20.319
Haven't you received a Divine Blessing?

00:07:20.480 --> 00:07:21.240
Divine Blessing?

00:07:22.720 --> 00:07:23.560
What's a Divine Blessing?

00:07:23.560 --> 00:07:26.720
A voice will appear deep in your heart

00:07:27.000 --> 00:07:28.160
reciting some words

00:07:29.120 --> 00:07:29.959
A voice?

00:07:30.839 --> 00:07:31.519
Yeah, there is

00:07:32.319 --> 00:07:33.439
Say the words out loud

00:07:33.759 --> 00:07:34.319
Okay

00:07:46.439 --> 00:07:47.199
Didn't memorize it.

00:07:50.120 --> 00:07:51.560
I admit you're all strong.

00:07:51.839 --> 00:07:52.959
Among mortals,

00:07:53.319 --> 00:07:54.839
you're the top of the top.

00:07:55.879 --> 00:07:57.360
In my current state,

00:07:58.199 --> 00:07:59.639
killing you all

00:08:00.120 --> 00:08:01.040
isn't possible.

00:08:02.079 --> 00:08:03.959
But I can kill a few before fleeing.

00:08:04.800 --> 00:08:06.639
Once I absorb your Dharma Forms

00:08:06.759 --> 00:08:07.879
and restore my strength,

00:08:08.560 --> 00:08:10.879
then, one by one,

00:08:11.079 --> 00:08:12.720
I will slaughter you all.

00:08:13.439 --> 00:08:15.040
Fuxi, Yang Jian...

00:08:15.199 --> 00:08:16.600
I'm really curious.

00:08:17.279 --> 00:08:18.879
If I absorb your Dharma Forms,

00:08:19.519 --> 00:08:20.680
just how high

00:08:21.439 --> 00:08:23.680
will my limits rise?

00:08:25.120 --> 00:08:25.800
San Gou.

00:08:26.519 --> 00:08:27.759
Get Tongtong out of here.

00:08:28.120 --> 00:08:28.920
How about

00:08:29.079 --> 00:08:29.879
you all leave?

00:08:30.160 --> 00:08:31.040
I guarantee

00:08:31.399 --> 00:08:32.919
he won't walk out of this warehouse.

00:08:33.639 --> 00:08:34.480
You planted bombs?

00:08:34.879 --> 00:08:35.919
Just tossed a few around.

00:08:36.519 --> 00:08:38.919
Barely enough to send this warehouse

00:08:39.039 --> 00:08:40.240
flying about ten meters up.

00:08:40.320 --> 00:08:41.679
Then you'll die with him.

00:08:41.759 --> 00:08:43.200
But blowing up an Immortal...

00:08:43.200 --> 00:08:43.960
that's pretty cool.

00:08:43.960 --> 00:08:44.559
No way.

00:08:48.480 --> 00:08:49.840
If they can't hold him off,

00:08:50.120 --> 00:08:50.840
you step in.

00:08:52.159 --> 00:08:54.360
It's our only chance to befriend Black Street.

00:08:54.639 --> 00:08:55.799
And there's also an Immortal here.

00:08:56.440 --> 00:08:57.840
If we can capture him alive,

00:08:58.159 --> 00:08:59.799
he'll give us tons of intel.

00:09:00.799 --> 00:09:02.440
That way Shanhai City's future

00:09:02.720 --> 00:09:03.840
will be much smoother.

00:09:03.960 --> 00:09:05.480
But by reputation,

00:09:06.039 --> 00:09:07.519
isn't Black Street just a bunch of thugs?

00:09:09.120 --> 00:09:09.879
Trust me.

00:09:10.519 --> 00:09:11.720
If this world

00:09:11.840 --> 00:09:13.279
keeps going down this path,

00:09:13.440 --> 00:09:14.240
good and evil

00:09:14.879 --> 00:09:16.399
will be impossible to define.

00:09:20.840 --> 00:09:21.840
I'm right here.

00:09:22.320 --> 00:09:24.320
It's not your turn to rush to your deaths.

00:09:34.480 --> 00:09:35.279
Oh no.

00:09:36.159 --> 00:09:37.320
Did I come too late?

00:09:46.080 --> 00:09:47.159
You've got nerve showing up.

00:09:53.000 --> 00:09:53.720
Hello.

00:09:55.360 --> 00:09:56.360
I'm the Madman.

00:09:56.600 --> 00:09:57.279
You were looking for me?

00:10:04.799 --> 00:10:05.919
What just happened?

00:10:06.399 --> 00:10:07.919
Did somebody just kick me flying?

00:10:08.320 --> 00:10:09.480
Just now?

00:10:10.360 --> 00:10:11.639
Just now...

00:10:12.240 --> 00:10:13.720
Was that Past in the Wind?

00:10:17.639 --> 00:10:18.600
Shanhai City,

00:10:19.159 --> 00:10:21.000
Liu Family, Liu Chengfeng.

00:10:22.519 --> 00:10:23.039
That's right.

00:10:23.440 --> 00:10:24.240
That's the name.

00:10:24.679 --> 00:10:25.320
By the way,

00:10:25.960 --> 00:10:26.759
do you have the surveillance footage?

00:10:27.320 --> 00:10:28.840
The footage from when Shen Hou died.

00:10:28.960 --> 00:10:29.759
I want to see it.

00:10:29.799 --> 00:10:32.519
I did pull the footage from that moment,

00:10:32.720 --> 00:10:34.279
but by the rules,

00:10:34.399 --> 00:10:35.360
outsiders can't view it.

00:10:39.679 --> 00:10:40.600
However,

00:10:40.720 --> 00:10:41.519
this foot...

00:10:41.519 --> 00:10:42.759
You dare threaten Mr. Liu?

00:10:43.639 --> 00:10:44.320
Yang Jian!

00:10:48.639 --> 00:10:49.759
I wasn't finished.

00:10:49.840 --> 00:10:50.919
I was saying that I

00:10:50.919 --> 00:10:51.519
just want to...

00:10:52.519 --> 00:10:53.360
keep living.

00:10:53.559 --> 00:10:55.000
No need for that, no need!

00:10:55.120 --> 00:10:55.720
You can see it.

00:10:55.720 --> 00:10:56.879
The footage is available.

00:10:56.919 --> 00:10:57.759
You can see it, you can see it.

00:10:58.080 --> 00:10:59.480
Go ahead, go ahead, take a look.

00:11:02.759 --> 00:11:03.279
I...

00:11:08.600 --> 00:11:10.120
Two battles, two defeats.

00:11:10.399 --> 00:11:12.679
How is he the strongest in Shanhai City?

00:11:13.759 --> 00:11:14.720
The opponents were stronger.

00:11:14.720 --> 00:11:15.320
Keep your voice down.

00:11:16.279 --> 00:11:16.799
Right.

00:11:25.440 --> 00:11:26.080
Thanks.

00:11:35.399 --> 00:11:36.480
What just happened?

00:11:37.080 --> 00:11:39.200
Was I just kicked across the room?

00:11:40.240 --> 00:11:41.559
Just now...

00:11:42.240 --> 00:11:43.720
Just now...

00:11:45.320 --> 00:11:47.399
Just now, you made Su Yang

00:11:47.399 --> 00:11:49.360
feel his life was in danger.

00:11:49.679 --> 00:11:51.559
That's why he gave it his all.

00:11:52.200 --> 00:11:52.960
In truth,

00:11:54.879 --> 00:11:56.080
you're no weaker than him.

00:11:57.240 --> 00:11:58.200
The two of you

00:11:58.399 --> 00:12:01.039
were like two master swordsmen dueling.

00:12:01.200 --> 00:12:02.799
Victory is decided in a single instant.

00:12:02.960 --> 00:12:03.639
It looked like

00:12:03.759 --> 00:12:05.799
you were completely crushed by him.

00:12:05.799 --> 00:12:06.799
But in reality,

00:12:07.120 --> 00:12:09.639
if he had slipped up in that instant,

00:12:09.799 --> 00:12:11.000
the outcome could have gone either way.

00:12:11.399 --> 00:12:12.240
Do you understand?

00:12:14.519 --> 00:12:15.279
Swordsman.

00:12:16.080 --> 00:12:16.919
I see.

00:12:18.799 --> 00:12:19.720
So that's how it is.

00:12:23.279 --> 00:12:23.840
Hello.

00:12:24.279 --> 00:12:25.120
I'm the Madman.

00:12:25.480 --> 00:12:26.120
You're looking for me?

00:12:27.960 --> 00:12:28.960
Su Yang.

00:12:34.000 --> 00:12:34.799
That's right.

00:12:36.159 --> 00:12:36.960
You are...

00:12:37.440 --> 00:12:38.039
an Immortal.

00:12:38.639 --> 00:12:39.320
Naturally.

00:12:39.759 --> 00:12:40.559
This Immortal

00:12:41.519 --> 00:12:42.279
is Zi Shu.

00:12:44.000 --> 00:12:45.320
You killed someone from our Clinic.

00:12:45.559 --> 00:12:46.840
According to the rules of our Clinic,

00:12:47.279 --> 00:12:48.679
we'll torture you for a week,

00:12:48.879 --> 00:12:49.840
and only then let you die.

00:12:51.679 --> 00:12:54.080
Hasn't it always been just you and Tongtong at the Clinic?

00:12:54.799 --> 00:12:56.519
Since when was there such a rule?

00:12:56.639 --> 00:12:57.200
Just now.

00:12:58.080 --> 00:12:58.720
And besides,

00:12:59.200 --> 00:13:00.519
our Clinic has three people.

00:13:01.000 --> 00:13:02.399
Are you talking about

00:13:02.840 --> 00:13:03.879
that Fake Shen Hou?

00:13:04.480 --> 00:13:06.360
Ignorant, foolish mortal.

00:13:06.480 --> 00:13:08.159
How dare you raise a hand against an Immortal.

00:13:08.840 --> 00:13:11.120
If you push open that door right now,

00:13:11.360 --> 00:13:12.200
perhaps

00:13:12.679 --> 00:13:15.120
I'll let you die a quicker death.

00:13:15.879 --> 00:13:16.679
Mortal.

00:13:16.919 --> 00:13:17.720
Immortal.

00:13:19.200 --> 00:13:21.639
Today, I'll do it his way

00:13:22.039 --> 00:13:23.480
to finish what he couldn't.

00:13:25.519 --> 00:13:26.279
A stick.

00:13:27.279 --> 00:13:28.240
I should have one too.

00:13:30.039 --> 00:13:31.159
Hand me a stick.

00:13:38.600 --> 00:13:39.200
Sorry,

00:13:39.480 --> 00:13:40.159
give me a moment.

00:13:45.919 --> 00:13:48.360
Guess that last kick didn't hurt enough, huh?

00:13:49.240 --> 00:13:50.320
Still haven't learned your lesson.

00:13:53.440 --> 00:13:55.639
Why should we be ordered around by him?

00:13:55.879 --> 00:13:57.279
You've got a point.

00:13:57.720 --> 00:13:59.720
But let's just do as he says.

00:13:59.840 --> 00:14:00.879
Yeah, yeah.

00:14:00.919 --> 00:14:03.600
If he goes mad, he really will destroy the Immortal Gate.

00:14:16.799 --> 00:14:18.840
Another of Shen Hou's Divine Blessing recipients.

00:14:19.480 --> 00:14:22.279
Since I devoured his first Soul Fragment,

00:14:22.440 --> 00:14:24.120
I can devour his second one too.

00:14:24.120 --> 00:14:25.799
You're nothing but nourishment to me.

00:14:26.440 --> 00:14:29.000
I'll personally make you push open the Immortal Gate,

00:14:29.600 --> 00:14:30.840
then send you on your way.

00:14:44.240 --> 00:14:45.639
So annoying.

00:15:12.440 --> 00:15:13.000
No!

00:15:13.440 --> 00:15:14.320
You can't kill me.

00:15:14.679 --> 00:15:15.440
I'm an Immortal.

00:15:15.720 --> 00:15:16.879
I'm in Heavenly Court's Celestial Registry.

00:15:17.399 --> 00:15:18.919
Killing me would violate Heavenly Law.

00:15:19.559 --> 00:15:20.399
This strike

00:15:22.440 --> 00:15:23.879
is for Tongtong.

00:15:34.879 --> 00:15:37.399
The footage is 487 seconds total.

00:15:38.080 --> 00:15:39.519
For the remaining 481,

00:15:39.960 --> 00:15:40.960
we'll go back

00:15:41.240 --> 00:15:43.080
and take our time with a scalpel.